{"tid":1232473,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電視或直播新聞台可信度調查結果–2019年第2季","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:51:18.000Z","uid":123289,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79c0e854e8bdce064797ad05a4ba7d39e606cc0d","tid":1232473,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"首先，感謝大家投票支持！<br />\n<br />\n港台電視成為本次調查大贏家，得分高達9.93分，成功成為香港最受信任的電視或直播新聞台。<br />\nnow TV (viu TV)及有線電視亦分別獲得9.84分(9.86分)及9.81分之佳績。<br />\n立場新聞分數亦高達9.54。<br />\n另一方面東方日報分數只有0.17分。<br />\n本次投票中，獲得最多選票的電視或直播新聞台為無線電視，總共有795票，成為本次投票票王！無視電視的得分則只有0.06分(10分為滿分)。<br />\n<br />\n評分表，票數以6月16日下午11時為準。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nKmW12Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKmW12Q.jpg&h=b1be1732&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n投票連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1211484/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1211484/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ef8b684180ae5c9ebce50e8bdad3ed2eea56d38e","tid":1232473,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872417948e1d24adce3a7a81b6b4a6b8cc25b0c8","tid":1232473,"uid":137706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"未入黎已經估到CCTVB排第尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac031783e6446cc86778c1802bce6e072a2c642","tid":1232473,"uid":116785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"最高分係無綫最低分又無綫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9149b94c33a8b8dd478acfa5cbed44164d71e6d","tid":1232473,"uid":123289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fac031783e6446cc86778c1802bce6e072a2c642","tid":1232473,"uid":116785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"最高分係無綫最